title: Ithaca Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Salad bar, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu is meat-heavy but also includes some labeled vegetarian and vegan items. Vegans could get tofutti cream cheese, soy or almond milk, seitan panini, and tofu scramble. A full salad and hot foods bar, fresh baked bread. Has Wi-Fi.
